<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ez-Buy - Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand mt-2 mt-lg-0" href="#">
                <img src="/logo/logo-no-background.svg" height="50" alt="Logo" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse">
                <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Register</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/store">Store</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/categories">Categories</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/cart">Cart</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <form action="/search" method="POST" class="d-flex">
                <input type="search" class="form-control rounded" placeholder="Search" aria-label="Search"
                    aria-describedby="search-addon" name="search">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-search"></i></button>
            </form>
            <form action="/logout" method="GET" class="d-flex cardmarginleft">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Logout</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="username-container desktop">
            <span class="username">{{username}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="username-container mobile">
            <span class="username">{{username}}</span>
        </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <main>
        <section class="welcome-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="welcome-title">Welcome to Our E-Shop, {{username}}!</h1>
                <p class="welcome-text">
                    At our E-Shop, we are dedicated to providing you with the best online shopping experience. We value
                    the trust you place in us, which is why we prioritize security and privacy. Our secure payment
                    gateways ensure that your transactions are protected, allowing you to shop with confidence. Your
                    personal information is handled with utmost care, and we strictly adhere to industry standards to
                    safeguard your data.
                </p>
                <p class="welcome-text">
                    Stay updated with the latest trends, promotions, and exclusive offers by subscribing to our
                    newsletter. Be the first to know about new arrivals, special discounts, and exciting sales events.
                    Join our vibrant community of satisfied customers who have discovered the convenience and joy of
                    shopping at our E-Shop.Thank you for choosing us as your preferred online shopping destination.
                    Start exploring now and find exactly what you're looking for. Happy shopping!
                    add this in html and css elements to make it display nicely on my website's home page

                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h4>Subscribe to Our Newsletter</h4>
                    <p>Stay updated with the latest trends, promotions, and exclusive offers by subscribing to our
                        newsletter. Be the first to know about new arrivals, special discounts, and exciting sales
                        events.</p>
                    <form>
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Your Email Address" required>
                            <div class="input-group-append">
                                <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Subscribe</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h4>Contact Us</h4>
                    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to our customer support
                        team. We are here to help!</p>
                    <ul class="contact-info">
                        <li><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i> Email: d.arethas@mc-class.gr</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> Phone: +306984262074</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>